---

## Objective

Replace the TODO stub in `sendSlackNotification()` with a working implementation that sends a rich formatted message to a Slack Incoming Webhook URL. Messages include color-coded attachments (red for failures, green for success, yellow for rollbacks), project context, error details, and a link to the dashboard.

---

